precis:
Amendments to the SHIP'S TONNAGE SURVEY AND MEASUREMENT FEES REGULATIONS
which, effective June 1, 1994, increase most of the existing fees by
29.7% for the survey and measurement of a ships' tonnage, that being the
cumulative rate of inflation since the last increase in 1985.
